<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="whatever-adj">whatever <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /wɒt'evə(r)/    美 /wət'evər/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>任何；无论什么；不管什么：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She would tell him whatever news she got. 
她得到任何消息都会告诉他。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Whatever dictionary you have, lend it to me. 
不管你有什么字典，借给我。</p></div></div>